# Demo for others..  I'm going to set some hotkeys that may clash with osx hotkeys because I'm a curmodgeon and the way I've always done it is absolutely the best ;)

cmd + ctrl - f : yabai -m space --layout float
cmd + ctrl - n : yabai -m space --layout bsp

